      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor signs of use, such as small stone chips on the front bumper and very light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is tidy and all major features are fully functional. This is a solid, dependable car that has been cared for properly and is ready for the road.",
