    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a functional, high-mileage daily driver. The exterior shows its history with several visible scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear fender. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. While the engine runs reliably, the vehicle will soon require a routine tune-up and the tires are nearing the end of their tread life. It is a dependable car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
