      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This beauty is in wonderful shape and ready for its next adventure! It drives like a dream, looks fantastic, and has been super dependable for me. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value\u2014honestly, it\u2019s just a solid, honest car that\u2019s ready to hit the road. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
