      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers its power through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a rod bearing service utilizing VAC coated bearings and ARP bolts. The Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system is fully operational, providing variable compression and rebound settings to suit the tarmac. Recent service includes a comprehensive throttle actuator overhaul and a fresh fill of 10W-60 synthetic lubricant. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with 'good' condition, the mechanical vitals are optimized for high-RPM performance. A true driver's specification with the carbon fiber roof and a clean subframe inspection.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
