    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish and deep color, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful use. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Moving inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The upholstery shows minimal wear, with only light softening of the leather on the driver's seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment screen, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. I have kept a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance, including a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. This is a solid, honest car that offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
